long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
100% FREE! 

Schedule WhatsApp Message extension allows users to schedule messages to be sent from WhatsApp Web. 

With this extension, users can easily set the time and date for their messages to be sent, ensuring that their important messages are sent out on time. 

Can be used for:
✅ Birthday/Anniversary greetings
✅ Client reminders
✅ Follow ups
✅ Special events 
✅ More

The extension also allows users to easily review their scheduled messages, making it easy to stay organized. 

This extension is perfect for those who need to keep track of their messages and send them out at the right time.
